  "texts": [
    "Second language learners must select the most appropriate strategy based on individual characteristics to achieve an efficient and successful vocabulary learning process.",
    "This study demonstrates, using a questionnaire survey and quantitative analysis, that the varied academic levels of Chinese college students impact the techniques they choose to acquire language.",
    "Chinese college students choose the metacognitive strategy above the others.",
    "It is possible that learners gradually obtain more confidence in their capacity to acquire vocabulary at this age in college students.",
    "Learners attempt to explore new vocabulary learning routines according to their current situation and assist them in gathering vocabulary according to their comprehension rather than depending solely on rote memorization."
  ],
